de.ryanthara.ja.rycon.io

Class LineWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ryanthara.ja.rycon.io.LineWriter

  • public class LineWriter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class writes an ArrayList<String> line by line to a file.

    A couple of things are implemented as additional functionality. At the moment, there is no thread safety implemented or planed.
